Cell["\<\
I found a solution to these problems on \
https://github.com/FeynCalc/feyncalc/issues/93
A general cheat-sheet of all QFT scattering can be found in \
https://arxiv.org/pdf/1602.04182\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.967655383491758*^9, 3.967655449038912*^9}, 
